      "overview": "UPS engaged Anglepoint for a comprehensive IBM software asset management assessment covering up to 250 IBM products across 70,000 servers, 270,000 workstations, 5 physical mainframes, and 10,000 Red Hat servers. The engagement identified $8.9M in total optimization opportunities through license compliance analysis and cost savings recommendations.",
